{"tid":2460756,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"長榮貨輪擱淺蘇伊士運河第3天 估計全球貿易每小時損失4億美元","createTime":"2021-03-25T04:42:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T05:59:48.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"dd5435366f049148f677164b8610ed98a68cc60f","tid":2460756,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一艘隸屬於長榮海運的貨櫃輪「長賜輪」（Ever Given）23日擱淺在蘇伊士運河，造成雙向航道阻塞，嚴重影響各國船運，塞船情形已進入第3天，目前「長賜輪」仍未脫困，現約185艘船正在等候通過運河，初估運河阻塞將致全球貿易每小時損失4億美元。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n隨著阻塞時間越來越長，等候穿越運河的船隻也越來越多，現約有185艘船受阻，包含郵輪、貨輪、天然氣運輸船等，知名船舶報《Lloyd's List》估計運河阻塞將致全球貿易每小時損失4億美元。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭船舶工程巨頭、荷蘭皇家Boskalis的子公司「Smit Salvage」（SMIT），派遣10人精英團隊已搭機於週四凌晨2點抵達當地<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3478449\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3478449&d=G6FzB8XOFkGMVaf%2BSD5%2FxrzLFaoPUDMH8GO3Y0uvk74%3D&h=a54be4a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3478449&h=c97fdb4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3478449</a>"},{"pid":"92eced76d25d8f89a8fb2db5053e152743ec9c14","tid":2460756,"uid":262746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:43:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">又要跌啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"403185ae9aba6c2f6a60320689a8a7cea507b738","tid":2460756,"uid":52675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"諗起入錯油潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb57b471f5c31096f817909197242304d0737212","tid":2460756,"uid":257369,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"403185ae9aba6c2f6a60320689a8a7cea507b738","tid":2460756,"uid":52675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"諗起入錯油潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"體細節係點唔記得好清楚，唔知有冇人搵得返個post。 成件事大概係咁： 巴打喺一間物流公司做，負責幫貨船入油。果日有架船要出航遠行，咁巴打就一如往常咁打滿佢，送佢一程。過左一段時間巴打就發現今次HiHi嘞，原來架船係用柴油嘅，點知佢一時錯手入左汽油。其實入錯油都冇咩，架船又唔會因為咁爆炸死人嘅；最多都係死火，啲貨就遲幾日到。不過公司就要賠錢，而佢都有俾人炒嘅心理準備。我諗佢當時都仲心存一絲希望，希望架船聽聽話話，捱到去終站。 不過架船真係喺太平洋島嶼擱淺左。巴打心諗出得嚟行，預左要還，已經準備定執包袱。果然好快就收到消息，不過炒嘅唔單止係佢，而係成個部門十幾人，連上司嘅上司都俾人炒埋。點解呢？ 原來係架船上面係載住一啲化學物品，擱淺之後洩漏到成個海都係，公司要負責處理污染物，一賠賠幾億。而事件裡面最無辜嘅係附近一個水清沙幼嘅太平洋小島，因為生態災害，要即時封鎖隔離。 就因為遠在香港嘅巴打一時錯手，將一個太平洋小島毀於一旦。"},{"pid":"eaccfd4bcc84b2bc67359babaa35444dc1e83085","tid":2460756,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"係咪特登㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3082a870575fa797efc69447d19d42dbff9bc63a","tid":2460756,"uid":330227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaccfd4bcc84b2bc67359babaa35444dc1e83085","tid":2460756,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"係咪特登㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攬炒"},{"pid":"0ab5e77f8ebc4e798962ebc01ea2c8e4678c29f3","tid":2460756,"uid":119347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T04:53:43.000Z","msg":"堵路暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2784a5ac6b2a1e7f5451c54a8dd6304e9f1472","tid":2460756,"uid":360041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T05:03:03.000Z","msg":"搞咁多做咩 遲早又塞番<br />\n起多條咪算"},{"pid